- src/renderer/index.html (add selector)
- src/renderer/renderer.js (mode switching logic)
- src/renderer/styles.css (styling)

## EXPECTED RESULT
1. Load a model
2. Select Wireframe -> see only edges
3. Select X-Ray -> see transparent model
4. Select Solid -> back to normal

